last_episode_to_air.overview: Jeong-hwan is tasked with dismantling the GK Technology Innovative Vision Room once and for all. Bok-gi and Jae-wook put the past behind them.

name: Private Lives
overview: In a world where data is no longer private, con artists uncover a sinister surveillance scheme headed by the government and a greedy corporation.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Growing up witnessing her parents con and be conned, Cha Joo-eun tries on many hats while embarking on a rugged path of her own.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Jeong Bok-gi proves to be a formidable opponent. While working a new gig, Joo-eun meets Lee Jeong-hwan, who unexpectedly sweeps her off her feet.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: As Joo-eun looks for answers, the story behind Jeong-hwan's veiled identity is told through his first interactions with Sophia Chung and Kim Jae-wook.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: After her love life goes up in smoke, Joo-eun retraces Jeong-hwan's final steps and becomes acquainted with people and places from his real life.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Snippets of Jeong-hwan’s double life are revealed during his final mission involving Bok-gi, Jae-wook and a much-sought-after ledger.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Jeong-hwan keeps a close eye on people he once trusted. With a common goal in mind, Bok-gi draws up a win-win scenario to earn Joo-eun's partnership.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: Jae-wook approaches Kim Sang-man with a plan to channel their influence into power, stemming from a bloodstained encounter dating back 20 years.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Through their networks and expertise, Joo-eun and Jeong-hwan uncover explosive details about each other's true identities.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: Jae-wook schemes to get rid of Jeong-hwan and Joo-eun and further his political agenda in one fell swoop. Jeong-hwan shows his face to Joo-eun.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: Joo-eun gains an unlikely ally. Tapping into remnants from past relationships, Bok-gi finds answers about Jae-wook's true motives.

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: Leveraging his knowledge of Jae-wook's strategy, Jeong-hwan secures a meeting with the opposing candidate. Joo-eun takes action to clear her name.

episodes.name: Episode 12
episodes.overview: Kim Sang-man presents Jeong-hwan with answers and an ultimatum. Determined to get even with Jae-wook, Bok-gi goes after his target.

episodes.name: Episode 13
episodes.overview: Much to Jae-wook's surprise, Bok-gi introduces herself as the newest member of the campaign team. Joo-eun grows suspicious of Jeong-hwan's past.

episodes.name: Episode 14
episodes.overview: Bok-gi paints Yoo Byung-jun in a positive light, while Jae-wook deploys his people to bring down their opponent. A key witness comes out of hiding.

episodes.name: Episode 15
episodes.overview: New evidence brings a traitor to the surface and takes competitors out of the running. Sang-man sets a trap for Jeong-hwan and Jae-wook.

episodes.name: Episode 16
episodes.overview: Jeong-hwan is tasked with dismantling the GK Technology Innovative Vision Room once and for all. Bok-gi and Jae-wook put the past behind them.
